com.hamweather.aeris.model

Class AerisPermissionsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hamweather.aeris.model.AerisPermissionsBuilder

  • public class AerisPermissionsBuilder
extends Object
    Builder to obtain an AerisPermissions object based on certain criteria. Anything not added to the builder with a withXXX() call when build() is called will be defaulted to false.
